    modified_response: "I will now implement the `/src/components/Activity.tsx` component. It replicates the custom timeline activity feed, including the wave element in the \"October Savings\" indicator card. It supports filtering charging types (Smart Charging, Commutes or Travel, and Supercharger station events) and provides a layout to initiate logging a new charge."
