  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Celebrating Flawless Execution**\n\nThe application is compiling and launching beautifully! It\'s fantastic to see all the tools running flawlessly. I\'m focusing now on perfectly summarizing the work, following all communication guidelines, and maintaining a friendly and helpful AI Assistant voice.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed building the Volt electric vehicle savings and smart analytics platform. Below is the design and functional overview of the fully interactive, responsive application:\n\n### Brand & Design Concept\n- **Minimalist Dark Canvas**: Follows a modern dark aesthetic based on a deep navy and slate color theme. It uses generous spacing and sharp structural layering to maintain high readability and focus.\n- **Dynamic Accents**: Incorporates a dual-font strategy, utilizing **Inter** for standard readable user interface elements paired with **JetBrains Mono** for all monospaced numerical data, currencies, and technical measurements.\n- **Electric green and golden tints** highlight savings curves and solar-focused activities.\n\n### Core Modules Integrated\n- **Lifetime Savings Dashboard**:\n  - Displays dynamic live aggregations of **Lifetime Capital Saved**, **Petrol Avoided (L)**, and **CO2 Emission Reductions (tons)** with a pulsating state indicator context.\n  - Interactive **Savings Growth Area & Line chart** incorporating glowing gradient curves, tooltips, and horizontal timeline filters (YTD, 6 Months, and 3-Month ranges).\n  - Quick-glance cards showing dynamic calculated indices, electricity consumption, and fuel price tracking.\n- **Interactive Log Charging Module**:\n  - Implements field states for logging new events. Includes date pickers, target location descriptors, energy input (kWh), and financial bills ($).\n  - Integrated a **Smart Estimator** that estimates charging costs based on active grid tariff conditions.\n  - Features a clean **Solar Energy Used** toggle switch which zeroes out charging billing offsets to reflect local zero-emission generation.\n- **Timeline Activity Ledger**:\n  - Lists and groups sessions under dynamic calendar indicators (*Today*, *Yesterday*, or structured historical dates).\n  - Highlights specific vehicle charging types (*Home Smart Charging*, *DC Fast Chargers*, and *Commute Trip logs*), color-coded with customized visual components.\n  - Supports quick timeline item deletions.\n- **Vehicles Telemetry & Registries**:\n  - Displays real-time synced diagnostics (SoC %, range capacities, and odometer milestones) styled inside a bento grid structure with circular geometric overlays.\n  - Features an interactive **\"Force Sync Data\"** action that updates diagnostic properties in real time.\n  - Includes a model registering wizard allowing users to easily select popular manufacturers (such as *Tesla*, *Tata*, *MG*, or *Hyundai*) or input their own vehicle metrics manually.\n- **Assumptions & Calibration Console**:\n  - Offers full customization over equivalent internal combustion engine benchmarks (Equivalent Liter consumption per 100km, local fuel price per Liter, CO2 output per km) to continuously maintain accurate calculations.\n  - Supports resetting to baseline benchmarks and erasing mock logs back to pristine presets.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      nanos: 401710375
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
